    "Proof of Work (PoW): PoW requires high network bandwidth, making it unsuitable for IoT applications.",
    "However, it is widely used in various platforms, so it is likely to be incorporated into healthcare services. 2.",
    "Proof of Stake (PoS): In this algorithm, the next block is mined by selecting a node through a lottery or random selection process.",
